<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es-MX">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<style>
  @page { margin: 30px 40px; size: letter; }
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: #0f172a; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.4; }

  .watermark {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    opacity: 0.06; z-index: -1; pointer-events: none;
    font-size: 120px; font-weight: 900; color: #1e40af;
    transform: rotate(-30deg);
    letter-spacing: 8px; white-space: pre;
  }

  .header { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .header img { height: 50px; }
  .header-center { text-align: center; flex: 1; }
  .header-center h1 { font-size: 18px; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .header-center h2 { font-size: 13px; color: #1e40af; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .header-center small { font-size: 7.5px; color: #475569; }

  .folio-line {
    text-align: center; font-size: 7.5px; color: #475569;
    padding: 4px 0 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #cbd5e1; margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #1e40af;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #1e40af;
    padding-bottom: 3px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .columns { display: flex; gap: 16px; }
  .col-left { flex: 1.6; }
  .col-right { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }

  .data-row { display: flex; margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .data-label { font-weight: 700; color: #0f172a; min-width: 130px; font-size: 10px; }
  .data-value { color: #334155; font-size: 10px; }

  .photo-frame {
    width: 142px; height: 80px; border: 1.5px solid #cbd5e1;
    border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; display: flex;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    background: #f8fafc; margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .photo-frame img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  .photo-placeholder { text-align: center; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 6px; padding: 4px; line-height: 1.3; }

  .qr-section { margin: 6px 0; text-align: center; }
  .qr-section img { width: 60px; height: 60px; }
  .qr-section small { display: block; color: #64748b; font-size: 5.5px; }
  .qr-placeholder { text-align: center; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 5.5px; line-height: 1.3; }

  .firma-section {
    margin-top: 6px; padding-top: 5px; border-top: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
    text-align: center; width: 100%;
  }
  .firma-section .title { font-weight: 700; font-size: 7px; color: #334155; }
  .firma-section .hash { font-size: 5.5px; color: #64748b; word-break: break-all; font-family: monospace; margin-top: 2px; }

  .sellos-grid {
    display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 30px; margin: 24px 0 12px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .sello { text-align: center; width: 150px; }
  .sello svg { width: 110px; height: 110px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .sello .sello-nombre { font-size: 8px; font-weight: 700; color: #0f172a; }
  .sello .sello-desc { font-size: 6.5px; color: #64748b; }

  .nota {
    font-size: 7.5px; color: #475569; text-align: justify;
    border-top: 1px solid #cbd5e1; padding-top: 10px; margin-top: 10px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .footer {
    border-top: 1px solid #cbd5e1; padding-top: 6px; margin-top: 18px;
    text-align: center; font-size: 6.5px; color: #94a3b8;
  }

  .historial-section { margin-top: 20px; }
  .historial-section h3 { font-size: 11px; color: #1e40af; border-bottom: 1px solid #cbd5e1; padding-bottom: 4px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 8px; }
  th { background: #1e40af; color: #fff; padding: 4px 6px; text-align: left; font-weight: 600; }
  td { padding: 3px 6px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; color: #334155; }
  tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #f8fafc; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="watermark">SIVACAD</div>

<div class="header">
  {{#if logo_tecnm}}<img src="{{logo_tecnm}}" alt="TecNM">{{/if}}
  <div class="header-center">
    <h1>KARDEX DEL ALUMNO</h1>
    <h2>SISTEMA INTEGRAL DE VALIDACIÓN Y CONTROL ACADÉMICO</h2>
    <small>SIVACAD — Tecnológico Nacional de México / TESI</small>
  </div>
  {{#if logo_tesi}}<img src="{{logo_tesi}}" alt="TESI">{{/if}}
</div>

<div class="folio-line">
  Folio: <strong>{{folio}}</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; Emitido: <strong>{{fecha_emision}}</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; Zona horaria: <strong>{{zona_horaria}}</strong>
</div>

<div class="section-title">DATOS DEL ALUMNO</div>

<div class="columns">
  <div class="col-left">
    <div class="data-row"><span class="data-label">Nombre Completo:</span><span class="data-value">{{alumno.nombre_completo}}</span></div>
    <div class="data-row"><span class="data-label">Matrícula:</span><span class="data-value">{{alumno.matricula}}</span></div>
    <div class="data-row"><span class="data-label">CURP:</span><span class="data-value">{{alumno.curp}}</span></div>
    <div class="data-row"><span class="data-label">Carrera:</span><span class="data-value">{{alumno.carrera}}</span></div>
    <div class="data-row"><span class="data-label">Semestre:</span><span class="data-value">{{alumno.semestre}}</span></div>
    <div class="data-row"><span class="data-label">Promedio General:</span><span class="data-value">{{alumno.promedio}}</span></div>
    <div class="data-row"><span class="data-label">Créditos Cubiertos:</span><span class="data-value">{{alumno.creditos_cubiertos}}</span></div>
    <div class="data-row"><span class="data-label">Estatus:</span><span class="data-value">{{alumno.estatus}}</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-right">
    <div class="photo-frame">
      {{#if url_foto}}
        <img src="{{url_foto}}" alt="Foto institucional">
      {{else}}
        <div class="photo-placeholder">
          Aquí se inserta la foto<br>institucional del alumno del<br>siguiente tamaño: 5 x 2.5cm
        </div>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
    <div class="qr-section">
      {{#if url_qr}}
        <img src="{{url_qr}}" alt="QR">
      {{else}}
        <div class="qr-placeholder">
          Aquí se inserta el código<br>QR y FIRMA ELECTRÓNICA<br>DEL SISTEMA SIVACAD<br>generado por el sistema<br>SIVACAD
        </div>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
    <div class="firma-section">
      <div class="title">FIRMA ELECTRÓNICA DEL SISTEMA SIVACAD</div>
      <div class="hash">SHA-256: {{firma_hash}}</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="sellos-grid">
  {{#each sellos}}
  <div class="sello">
    {{{img}}}
    <div class="sello-nombre">{{titulo}}</div>
    <div class="sello-desc">{{descripcion}}</div>
  </div>
  {{/each}}
</div>

<div class="nota">
  Si quieres visualizar o verificar qué materias acreditaste, estás en 2da oportunidad, si estás en
  recurse o te fuiste a materia especial, visita la plataforma oficial SIGAA (Sistema Integral de
  Gestión Académica y Administrativa) para más información. El link de la plataforma oficial es el
  siguiente: <strong>https://sigaa.tesi.org.mx/index.php</strong>
</div>

{{#if historial.length}}
<div class="historial-section">
  <h3>DETALLE ACADÉMICO — MATERIAS CURSADAS</h3>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Período</th>
        <th>Clave</th>
        <th>Materia</th>
        <th>Calificación</th>
        <th>Créditos</th>
        <th>Estado</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {{#each historial}}
      <tr>
        <td>{{periodo}}</td>
        <td>{{clave}}</td>
        <td>{{materia}}</td>
        <td>{{calificacion}}</td>
        <td>{{creditos}}</td>
        <td>{{estado}}</td>
      </tr>
      {{/each}}
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>
{{/if}}

<div class="footer">
  Documento generado electrónicamente el {{fecha_emision}} &nbsp;|&nbsp; Folio: {{folio}} &nbsp;|&nbsp;
  Zona horaria: {{zona_horaria}} &nbsp;|&nbsp; SIVACAD
</div>

</body>
</html>
